sequenceDiagram
    participant GW1 as Gateway A<br/>(dev workstation 1)
    participant GW2 as Gateway B<br/>(dev workstation 2)
    participant GW3 as Gateway C<br/>(CI runner)
    participant TS as Team Server<br/>(shared container)
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>(audit + config)

    Note over GW1,GW3: Peer Discovery (mDNS on LAN / static config for WAN)

    GW1->>GW2: mDNS probe: "who is neuralgentics-gateway?"
    GW2-->>GW1: "I am, peer ID: gw-b, version: 0.1.0"
    GW1->>GW3: mDNS probe
    GW3-->>GW1: "I am, peer ID: gw-c, version: 0.1.0"

    Note over GW1,GW3: Config Sync (Last-Writer-Wins with Vector Clocks)

    GW1->>GW1: Admin adds domain *.prefect.io to whitelist
    GW1->>GW2: gossip: config update {key: whitelist, val: *.prefect.io, clock: [A:1]}
    GW1->>GW3: gossip: config update {key: whitelist, val: *.prefect.io, clock: [A:1]}
    GW2->>GW2: merge: clock [A:1] > local [A:0], accept
    GW3->>GW3: merge: clock [A:1] > local [A:0], accept

    Note over GW1,TS: Audit Aggregation (Push to Team Server)

    GW1->>TS: POST /audit/batch {events: [...]}
    GW2->>TS: POST /audit/batch {events: [...]}
    GW3->>TS: POST /audit/batch {events: [...]}
    TS->>PG: INSERT INTO gateway_audit_log

    Note over TS: Team Server Down Scenario

    GW1->>TS: POST /audit/batch (fails)
    GW1->>GW1: buffer to local SQLite, retry every 30s
    TS-->>GW1: back online
    GW1->>TS: POST /audit/batch (flushed buffer)
